            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美光、達美航空盤前下跌;Five Below大漲",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XiB5xVhQQDW0sYGRm3OnTw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEE6414U_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 週四美國主要指數期貨小幅下跌,因全球油價在中東地區關鍵能源基礎設施遭遇一系列攻擊後飆升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間07:22(北京時間19:22),道瓊斯期貨下跌104點,跌幅0.2%,S&amp;P 500期貨下跌17點,跌幅0.3%,Nasdaq 100期貨下跌92點,跌幅0.4%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以下是今日盤前美股主要異動股:</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雪佛龍(Chevron)和埃克森美孚(Exxon Mobil)股價小幅上漲,此前伊朗對一處關鍵天然氣按金設施遭受的襲擊進行報復,轟炸了中東地區多處能源設施。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">達美航空(Delta Air Lines)和聯合航空(United Airlines)這兩隻對燃油成本上漲敏感的股票小幅下跌,郵輪運營商挪威郵輪控股(<span><span>Norwegian Cruise Line</span></span> Holdings)和嘉年華(Carnival)也出現下跌。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美光科技(Micron Technology)第二財季營收較去年同期增長近兩倍,每股收益增長近八倍,但該芯片製造商表示將在2026財年斥資超過250億美元建設新製造設施,比此前預測高出約50億美元,股價在盤前交易中下跌超過6%。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">SanDisk和西部數據(Western Digital)等存儲芯片股也走低,人工智能半導體巨頭英偉達同樣下跌。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">黃金連續第七日下跌,拖累紐蒙特(Newmont)、阿格尼科鷹礦(Agnico Eagle Mines)和自由港麥克莫蘭(Freeport-McMoRan)等金屬礦業股。由於市場預期利率將維持高位且美元走強,黃金的吸引力有所減弱,表現不佳。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Five Below股價大幅上漲,此前該零售商第一季度淨銷售額預測超出預期。</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%89-%E9%81%94%E7%BE%8E%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E7%9B%A4%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-five-below%E5%A4%A7%E6%BC%B2-124655360.html",
